UPDATE tabs_content 
SET isVisible = true, 
    htmlContent = '# Test Tab with Gradient

This tab has a CSS gradient background.

{{image1:center}}

The image above should be centered.'
WHERE documentId = 1 AND tabNumber = 1 AND backgroundType = 'gradient';
